            (The modal particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>呢</a> expresses that the action <a href='/word_detail.php?id=3995' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '睡覺 shuìjiào', 'to sleep')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>睡觉</a> is in progress.  An adverbial adjunct is not needed.)
          </p>
          <li>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '沒 méi', '(negative prefix for verbs) / have not / not')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">没</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3995' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '睡覺 shuìjiào', 'to sleep')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">睡觉</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=537' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kàn', 'to see / to look')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">看</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2543' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '書 shū', 'book')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">书</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a>。
            (He is not asleep, he is reading a book.)
            <p>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=7610' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fǒudìng', 'to negate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">否定</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=422' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'style, system, formula, rule')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">式</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '副詞 fùcí', 'adverb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">副词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '沒 méi', '(negative prefix for verbs) / have not / not')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">没</a>”。
              (The negative form uses the adverb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '沒 méi', '(negative prefix for verbs) / have not / not')" 
              onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>没</a>.)
            </p>
          </li>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='continuous'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動作 dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动作</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=710' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '持續 chíxù', 'to continue / to sustain')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">持续</a>
        The Continuous Aspect of an Action
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9307' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動態助詞 dòngtài zhùcí', 'aspectual particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动态助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=547' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhe', 'particle attached after verb to indicate action in progress')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">着</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動作 dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动作</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動作 dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动作</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2307' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '結果 jiéguǒ', 'outcome / result / conclusion')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">结果</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6241' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀態 zhuàngtài', 'status / state of affairs / state / mode')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状态</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=710' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '持續 chíxù', 'to continue / to sustain')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">持续</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4643' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動態 dòngtài', 'development / trend / dynamic state / movement')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动态</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2307' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '結果 jiéguǒ', 'outcome / result / conclusion')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">结果</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6241' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '狀態 zhuàngtài', 'status / state of affairs / state / mode')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">状态</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=500' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '發生 fāshēng', 'to happen / to occur / to take place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">发生</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1068' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '過去 guòqu', '(in the) past / former')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">过去</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=264' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '現在 xiànzài', 'at present / in the process of')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">现在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huòzhě', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或者</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2851' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '未來 wèilái', 'future')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">未来</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        The aspectual particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=547' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhe', 'particle attached after verb to indicate action in progress')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">着</a> expresses that an action or the result of an action is continuing.
        The state of an action or the result of an action can be in the past, present, or future.
        For example,
      </p>
