      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=335' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yào', 'to want ')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">要</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動作 dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动作</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1068' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '過去 guòqu', '(in the) past / former')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">过去</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4831' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '經歷 jīnglì', 'experience')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">经历</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9338' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '後面 hòumian', 'rear / back / behind / later / afterwards')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后面</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=367' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiā', 'add')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">加</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9307' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動態助詞 dòngtài zhùcí', 'aspectual particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动态助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=829' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '過 guò', 'to cross / to go over / to pass')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">过</a>”。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        To describe an experience in the past the aspectual particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1970' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '過 guò', 'particle to indicate experience')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>过</a> can be added after the predicate verb.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qù', 'to go')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">去</a><span class='hl'>过</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1559' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Shànghǎi', 'Shanghai')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上海</a>。
